flowchart TD
  AUTH[Ground-Signed Authorization]
  S3[SAFE-MODE S3]
  QUORUM[Evaluator Quorum]
  MUT[Apply Mutation M0-M4]
  LED[Mutation Ledger Entry]
  MON[Monitor Fault/Anomaly Rate]
  RB{Rollback?}

  AUTH --> S3 --> QUORUM --> MUT --> LED --> MON --> RB
  RB -->|yes| REVERT[Restore Prior Invariant Set]
  RB -->|no| DONE[Mutation Active]
